          <physDesc>
            <p>Paper, about 6 7/8 in. by 5 1/8, consisting of 140 leaves, some
                                    of which are much stained, and torn, especially foll. 1—4, 53,
                                    54, 121, and 136—140. The quires, signed with letters, were 15
                                    or 16 in number. Leaves are wanting at the beginning, as well as
                                    after foll. 4, 12 (one), 52 (one), and 136. There are from 18 to
                                    25 lines in each page. </p>
            <objectDesc form="codex">
                     <supportDesc material="chart">
                <extent>
                  <measure type="composition" unit="leaf" quantity="140">140 ff.</measure>
                </extent>
                        <condition>
